                    Five-door fastbacks might be the best of all worlds.                  </div>
                                                  <div class="credit">
                    <span class="icon icon-camera"></span>
                                          Audi                                      </div>
                              </figcaption>
                      </figure>
        </li>
              <li data-thumb="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-3-150x150.jpg" data-src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-3-scaled.jpg" data-responsive="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-3-980x653.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-3-1440x960.jpg 2560" data-sub-html="#caption-2040121">
