                              </figcaption>
                      </figure>
        </li>
              <li data-thumb="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-5-150x150.jpg" data-src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-5-scaled.jpg" data-responsive="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-5-980x735.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-5-1440x1080.jpg 2560" data-sub-html="#caption-2040118">
          <figure style="height:735px;">
            <div class="image" style="background-image:url('https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-5-980x735.jpg'); background-color:#000"></div>
