        </li>
              <li data-thumb="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-11-150x150.jpg" data-src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-11-scaled.jpg" data-responsive="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-11-980x735.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2025-Audi-A6-e-tron-11-1440x1080.jpg 2560" data-sub-html="#caption-2040113">
